I was casually meditating on 1 Corinthians 14, when I read some verses that I must have gone over, a gajillion times, mentally. Sometimes, I'm positive Paul must have had people hissing and cussing at him, when he spoke. 😕 I started out writing my thoughts on this one -- that's what I do with my @youversion bible app -- and it was turning into into a long note. So, I thought to share my thoughts with you. 🙂 I hope you enjoy reading the content & the chapter, as much as I did. 💜
